ấn bà nhiên) - 長相思其二（面蒼然，鬢皤然）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/T%E1%BB%B1-thu%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-ZK2gyS_M8jTP2EaEqWsE2w">Tự thuật kỳ 1 - 自述其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-T%E1%BA%AFc-T%E1%BB%AB/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-xu%E1%BA%A5t-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Quan-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-Gi%E1%BA%A3i-Qu%C3%A2n-ti%E1%BB%81n-b%E1%BB%91i-t%E1%BB%B1-Y-L%C3%AA-lai-th%C6%B0-ph%C3%BA-th%E1%BB%AD-kh%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-k%C3%BD-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-X9RoLtVOrpnvsp4HJY_FsQ">Tương xuất Ngọc Quan đắc Giải Quân tiền bối tự Y Lê lai thư phú thử khước ký kỳ 2 - 將出玉關得嶰筠前輩自伊犁來書賦此卻寄其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-T%E1%BA%AFc-T%E1%BB%AB/author-JAv5RkZakjKTfe65gwrmsQ">Lâm Tắc Từ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/%C6%AFu-l%C3%A3o/poem-qIyjHbe0mdIhfT_8koDJGA">Ưu lão - 憂老</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/author-5S8czaSOqXhHlNE7NtKr8g">Đặng Trần Côn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
